<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Registration Success</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #121212;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }
    .success-container {
      background-color: #1e1e1e;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .success-container h1 {
      color: #4caf50;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .success-container p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .success-container a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4caf50;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .success-container a:hover {
      background-color: #43a047;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-container">
    <h1>âœ… Payment Successful!</h1>
    <p>Your shop registration has been received and is now <strong>pending admin approval</strong>.</p>
    <p>You will be notified once your shop is activated.</p>
    <a href="/">Return to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
